 breast, treated with a right segmental mastectomy and right axillary lymph node dissection.\n\nRecommendations:  The patient’s surgical management is now complete.  She has a Medical Oncology consult 3/25/10, to discuss systemic therapies as indicated. Radiation Oncology consult to follow, to discuss required adjuvant breast irradiation.\n\n","mentions":[{"begin":1801,"end":1807,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_353","classUri":"Breast","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":90},{"begin":1506,"end":1511,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_342","classUri":"Right","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":80},{"begin":582,"end":587,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_307","classUri":"Lymph","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":80},{"begin":763,"end":773,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_312","classUri":"Metastatic","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":100},{"begin":407,"end":409,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_282","classUri":"M0StageFinding","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":80},{"begin":728,"end":736,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_310","classUri":"Axilla","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":100},{"begin":1289,"end":1297,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_330","classUri":"Swelling","negated":true,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":100},{"begin":1436,"end":1443,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_336","classUri":"StageII","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":95},{"begin":1543,"end":1562,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_346","classUri":"AxillaryLymphNode","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":100},{"begin":1552,"end":1557,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_348","classUri":"Lymph","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":80},{"begin":573,"end":603,"id":"fake_patient3_07072025191801_M_304","classUri":